Zadatak 1: Izbor prediktora¶

Za podatke iz data_1.csv, treba da sortirate prediktore od najboljeg do najgoreg, na 2 razlicita nacina:

1) na osnovu koeficijenata korelacije sa ciljnom promenljivom, 2) pomocu "omotac-algoritma", sa klasifikatorom po zelji.

Osmislite i nacrtajte grafik koji ilustruje kvalitete prediktora na po jednoj slici, za svaku od navedenih metoda.

data = pd.read_csv('data_1.csv').to_numpy()
X = data[:, 0:-1]
y = data[:, -1]

Korelacioni metod, korelacija sa ciljnom promenljivom¶

In [4]:
n = X.shape[-1]
Rxy = np.empty(shape=(n,))
for i in range(n):
    Rxy[i] = abs(np.corrcoef(x=X[::, i], y=y)[1, 0])
print("Most important feature based on coefficient of correlation (feature with label): ", np.argsort(-Rxy)+1)

Most important feature based on coefficient of correlation (feature with label):  [13  1 10  7  6  4 12  5  3  8  9  2 11]

plt.title("Feature importance (coefficient of correlation $x_i$ and $y$)")

"Omotac algoritam" (eng. Wraper algorithm)¶

In [6]:
from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score

selected_features = []
features_to_select = list(range(n))
selected_scores_mean = []
selected_scores_std = []
m = y.shape[-1]

while (len(features_to_select) != 0):
    val_scores_mean = []
    val_scores_std = []
    for i in features_to_select:
        model = DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=RANDOM_STATE)
        X_train = []
        for j in selected_features:
            X_train.append(X[:, j].reshape(m, 1))
        
        X_train.append(X[:, i].reshape(m, 1))
        X_train = np.array(X_train).reshape(m, len(selected_features)+1)
        # fitting and scoring
        scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y, cv=10, scoring='f1')
        val_scores_mean.append(np.mean(scores))
        val_scores_std.append(np.std(scores))
        
    selected_feature = features_to_select[np.argmax(np.array(val_scores_mean))]
    selected_scores_mean.append(np.max(np.array(val_scores_mean)))
    selected_scores_std.append(np.max(np.array(val_scores_std)))
    selected_features.append(selected_feature)
    features_to_select.pop(np.argmax(np.array(val_scores_mean)))

selected_features = np.array(selected_features)
selected_scores_mean = np.array(selected_scores_mean)
sort_ind = np.argsort(np.array(selected_features))

print("Most important feature based on wrapper feature selection method: ", selected_features+1)

Most important feature based on wrapper feature selection method:  [13  1  2  3  7  5 12 10  8  4 11  9  6]
In [7]:
plt.figure(figsize=FIGSIZE, dpi=DPI)
plt.plot(np.arange(n)+1, selected_scores_mean, label='mean score')
plt.fill_between(np.arange(n)+1, selected_scores_mean-selected_scores_std,
                 selected_scores_mean+selected_scores_std,facecolor='red',
                 alpha=ALPHA, label='$mean \\pm std$')
plt.xlabel("number of features")
plt.ylabel(r"score[f1 score]")
plt.title("Feature importance (f1 score)")
plt.grid(alpha=ALPHA)
plt.legend()

plt.tight_layout()

KOMENTAR: Rezultati primene obe metode su konzistentni oba algoritma su za dva najinformativnija prediktora izabrala $x_{13}$ i $x_1$.

Zadatak 2: Obucavanje stabla¶

Za jedan par prediktora iz data_1.csv obucite klasifikaciono stablo. Dozvoljeno je koriscenje ugradenih f-ja i klasa: sklearn.tree.DecisionTreeClassifier u Pythonu, odnosno ClassificationTree u Matlabu.

Osmislite i nacrtajte grafike koji demonstriraju uticaj maksimalne dubine (ili maksimalnog broja cvorova, ako biblioteka koju koristite ne omogucava zadavanje maksimalne dubine) na kvalitet dobijenog modela. Treba da ilustrujete 3 razlicita slucaja: kada je model podobucen, kada je preobucen, i kada nije ni podobucen ni preobucen. Prikazite i granice odlucivanja u ravni prediktora za svaki od ova 3 slucaja.

In [8]:
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.inspection import DecisionBoundaryDisplay

i1 = 8
i2 = 9

X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X[::, [i1, i2]],
                                                    y, random_state=RANDOM_STATE)

max_depth = [i for i in range(1,10)]

val_scores_mean = []
val_scores_std = []
for i in range(len(max_depth)):
    model = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=max_depth[i], random_state=RANDOM_STATE)
    scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv=10, scoring='f1')
    val_scores_mean.append(np.mean(scores))
    val_scores_std.append(np.std(scores))


max_depth = np.array(max_depth)
val_scores_mean = np.array(val_scores_mean)
val_scores_std = np.array(val_scores_std)

plt.figure(figsize=FIGSIZE, dpi=DPI)
plt.plot(max_depth, val_scores_mean, label='mean score')
plt.fill_between(max_depth, val_scores_mean-val_scores_std,
                 val_scores_mean+val_scores_std,facecolor='red',
                 alpha=ALPHA, label='$mean \\pm std$')
plt.xlabel("max depth")
plt.ylabel("score[f1 score]")
plt.title("Cross validation Decision Tree Classifier max depth")
plt.grid(alpha=ALPHA)
plt.legend()

plt.tight_layout()
In [9]:
#%% Plot for train set
max_depth = [1, 3, 5]


labels = np.unique(y)
plot_colors = "br"
plot_step = 0.02
n_classes = np.unique(y).shape[-1]
plt.figure(figsize=FIGSIZE, dpi=DPI)

for j in range(len(max_depth)):
    
    clf = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=max_depth[j],  random_state=RANDOM_STATE)
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    # Plot the decision boundary
    ax = plt.subplot(1,3,j+1)
    DecisionBoundaryDisplay.from_estimator(
        clf,
        X_train,
        cmap=plt.cm.coolwarm,
        response_method="predict",
        ax=ax,
        alpha = ALPHA
    )
    
    # Plot the training points
    for i, color in zip(range(n_classes), plot_colors):
        idx = np.where(y_train == i)
        plt.scatter(
            X_train[idx, 0],
            X_train[idx, 1],
            c=color,
            label= "class " + str(int(labels[i])),
        )
    
    ax.set_xlabel("$x_1$")
    ax.set_ylabel("$x_2$")
    ax.set_title("max depth: " + str(int(max_depth[j])))
    ax.grid(alpha=ALPHA)
    

plt.suptitle("Train samples")
plt.legend(loc="lower right")
plt.tight_layout()

Prikaz podobucavanja, dobro obucenog modela, i preobucenog modela na test skupu

In [10]:
#%% Plot for test set

max_depth = [1, 3, 5]

labels = np.unique(y)
plot_colors = "br"
plot_step = 0.02
n_classes = np.unique(y).shape[-1]
plt.figure(figsize=FIGSIZE, dpi=DPI)

for j in range(len(max_depth)):
    
    clf = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=max_depth[j],  random_state=RANDOM_STATE)
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    # Plot the decision boundary
    ax = plt.subplot(1,3,j+1)
    DecisionBoundaryDisplay.from_estimator(
        clf,
        X_test,
        cmap=plt.cm.coolwarm,
        response_method="predict",
        ax=ax,
        alpha = ALPHA
    )
    
    # Plot the test points
    for i, color in zip(range(n_classes), plot_colors):
        idx = np.where(y_test == i)
        plt.scatter(
            X_test[idx, 0],
            X_test[idx, 1],
            c=color,
            label= "class " + str(int(labels[i])),
        )
    
    ax.set_xlabel("$x_1$")
    ax.set_ylabel("$x_2$")
    ax.set_title("max depth: " + str(int(max_depth[j])))
    ax.grid(alpha=ALPHA)
    

plt.suptitle("Test samples")
plt.legend(loc="lower right")
plt.tight_layout()

KOMENTAR: Optimalan broj hiper-parametra maksimalna dubina stabla je dobijen krosvalidacijom na trening skupu za prediktore su izabrani $x_8$ i $x_9$ zbog lepseg prikaza. Na osnovu grafika i granice odlucivanja na trening i test podacima vidi se da je za vrednost hiper-parametra 1 doslo do podobucavanja odnsno granica odlucivanja je linearna, dok za vrednost hiper-parametra 5 doslo do preobucavanja, sto se slikovito vidi na graficima gde su prikazane granice odlucivanja, jer su se pojavile crvene oblasti gde bi trebalo da bude plava oblast, odnosno algoritam je pokusao da tacno klasifikuje sve crvene odbirke na test skupu i doslo je do preobucavanja.

Zadatak 3: Ansambli¶

Na podacima iz data_2.csv ispitajte kako hiper-parametri uticu na performanse sledeca dva algoritama: 1) Random Forest (RF) 2) Gradient Boosting (GB).

U oba algoritma koristite stabla odlucivanja kao clanove ansambla. Dozvoljeno je koriscenje ugradenih f-ja za obucavanje klasifikatora: fitcensemble (sa Method = LogitBoost) u Matlabu, odnosno RandomForestClassifier i GradientBoostingClassifier u Pyhon modulu sklearn.ensemble. Osmislite i nacrtajte grafike koji ilustruju uticaj hiper-parametara na kvalitet obucenog modela. Minimalan skup hiper-parametara koje treba da analizirate je

  • velicina ansambla,
  • velicina stabala,
  • maksimalan broj odlika koji se razmatraju pri dodavanju cvora stabla (za RF),
  • stopa ucenja (za GB).

Po zavrsenom treningu, graficki prikazite estimirane znacajnosti prediktora za bar jedan od dva analizirana algoritma.
